      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests and method-of-manufactured-solutions verification required for all governing equations.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification performed for momentum equations only; energy and species transport equations lack formal order-of-accuracy confirmation. Achieved level insufficient."
