      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation-based GCI on hemolysis index QoI across at least three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh refinement study performed; GCI on hemolysis index is 18%, exceeding the 5% threshold required at MRL 5. Achieved level 2."
