      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison of predicted vs. measured hemolysis index with uncertainty bounds at all 5 COU operating points.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index compared at 3 of 5 operating points; remaining 2 points lack experimental data. Metric-based comparison performed without full uncertainty propagation."
