      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation QoI must be the hemolysis index directly used in the regulatory decision, not a surrogate.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) used as QoI in validation activities, which is the direct regulatory metric. Relevance is high but spatial resolution of shear stress integration remains limited."
